## GDPR Compliance (EU Users)

For users in the European Union:

- **Data Controller**: There is no data controller because no personal data is collected
- **Legal Basis**: Not applicable (no data processing occurs)
- **Data Protection Officer**: Not required (no data collected)
- **Right to Complain**: Contact your local data protection authority if you have concerns

---

## CCPA Compliance (California Users)

For California residents:

- **Personal Information Sold**: None (we don't collect or sell any personal information)
- **Right to Know**: We don't collect any information about you
- **Right to Delete**: Uninstall the extension to remove all local data
- **Right to Opt-Out**: Not applicable (we don't sell data)

